  "2026-06-05T14:46:28.752Z",mcp-platform-subagent,"Derived the pm_run action list from canonical PM_TOOL_ACTIONS (imported from src/sdk/cli-contracts/enum-contracts.js). Added PM_RUN_ACTION_DESCRIPTION = `Operation name (one of): ${PM_TOOL_ACTIONS.join(', ')}. ` + trailing package-owned-dynamic-actions prose. Replaced the hand-maintained hardcoded action enumeration in the pm_run tool def with this constant, ending prose/enum drift. Trailing prose about dynamically-installed package actions preserved verbatim."
close_reason: "Shipped in pm-at83. The pm_run action-list description is now derived from the canonical PM_TOOL_ACTIONS enum via PM_RUN_ACTION_DESCRIPTION (`Operation name (one of): ` + PM_TOOL_ACTIONS.join(', ') + the package-owned dynamic-actions prose), replacing the hand-maintained hardcoded list so the MCP-facing description can no longer drift from the actual supported actions. The new handshake test asserts every PM_TOOL_ACTIONS entry appears in the description. Verified: full suite green + manual check."
